Package: cabsim-lv2
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libfftw3-single3
Description: VeJa Cabinet Simulator LV2 plugin (pistomp fork)
 Guitar cabinet impulse response convolver with 13 speaker models
 embedded as compiled data. Patched to support arbitrary JACK period
 sizes (64, 128, 256+) via a generalized overlap-add implementation.
